subject: Dear Sir
body:
Dear Sir
How are you doing today?Hope you are doing well
I have a business proposal that may interest you.
kindly reply back so that i will send your further details about the proposal.
waiting for your urgent response
Regards
Mr.Edward S. Ayensu

subject: Re: Dear Sir
body:
Dear S. Ayensu,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I hope this message finds you well. I am always open to hearing about new business proposals and opportunities. Could you please provide me with some more information about the proposal? What kind of business is it related to? How would I be involved?

I look forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Lucy
